      "sc:author": "Centers for Disease Control and Prevention",
      "sc:description": "MicrobeTrace is a web-based tool to visually render networks from surveillance, epidemiologic\ninvestigations, and genetic analyses. Using simple point-and-click interfaces, data can\nbe readily imported, integrated and visualized...no coding required!",
